{"tid":2189558,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"王永平反駁林鄭 「港無三權分立非事實」","createTime":"2020-09-05T03:40:09.000Z","updateTime":"2020-09-05T03:42:47.000Z","uid":25558,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"bd67ec1345a67f1903c90fa92021f002ce533c45","tid":2189558,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-05T03:40:09.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20200905/END3F6YDIBGHZKJGRPSING4GEM/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200905%2FEND3F6YDIBGHZKJGRPSING4GEM%2F&d=RlZLtXxvTyjhSejQ4AJs43O%2BoULzyGumsBrFMfYiBSk%3D&h=68d7a715\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200905%2FEND3F6YDIBGHZKJGRPSING4GEM%2F&h=1cf03a46\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20200905/END3F6YDIBGHZKJGRPSING4GEM/</a><br />\n<br />\n節錄<br />\n<br />\n王永平反駁林鄭 「港無三權分立非事實」<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/vqhSTHIQCbnnQwHeKJtmRbLkV1Q=/1329x886/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/HHF3GRDCVNHRHBE4P7K6EQPOYM.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FvqhSTHIQCbnnQwHeKJtmRbLkV1Q%3D%2F1329x886%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FHHF3GRDCVNHRHBE4P7K6EQPOYM.jpg&h=ca01574d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n王永平<br />\n<br />\n【本報訊】特首林鄭月娥與教育局長楊潤雄本周表明，香港沒三權分立，引起社會反彈。曾任問責局長的王永平撰文反駁，指林鄭稱香港沒三權分立的言論不是事實，王永平質疑林鄭否定香港有三權分立的客觀事實，同時亦不想學生認識香港有三權分立，圖順應中央強調對香港有全面管治權的立場，凡事講求政治正確。<br />\n<br />\n相關新聞：近七成市民促重啟立會選舉<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n斥特首只順應中央<br />\n<br />\n前公務員事務局局長的王永平在《AM730》撰文指，《基本法》下三權「不僅是分工，還可以互相制衡」，反問「把這種關係稱之為『三權分立』，有何不可？」再者即使香港特區行使的所有權力來自中央，中央亦只委任特首為特區之首，「但卻不等於行政機關以外的香港立法會和司法機構都要透過行政長官向中央負責」。<br />\n<br />\n王永平續指，《基本法》無規定立法會和司法機關須透過特首向中央負責，亦沒額外要求立法會和司法機關就日常工作或司法工作，直接或間接透過特首向中央負責。他強調，香港三權分立「不影響中央與特區的憲制關係，更符合《基本法》的具體條文」。<br />\n<br />\n王認為，港府這。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/r49PSQcz_GOUoRxuLNdhKV-jg6Y=/1329x886/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/POLJA4HHJFCTVHLPYFIUMG3WCQ.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2Fr49PSQcz_GOUoRxuLNdhKV-jg6Y%3D%2F1329x886%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FPOLJA4HHJFCTVHLPYFIUMG3WCQ.jpg&h=6e97cd7d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n林鄭月娥"},{"pid":"9f27b71ae00cbc08f1ab0d874e7037272fd36fad","tid":2189558,"uid":32667,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-05T03:41:19.000Z","msg":"關你撚事咩白頭佬，女皇的密令呀dllm"},{"pid":"7911938f17ecbc2b5ff840c6b84327fee7face7f","tid":2189558,"uid":155095,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"9f27b71ae00cbc08f1ab0d874e7037272fd36fad","tid":2189558,"uid":32667,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-05T03:41:19.000Z","msg":"關你撚事咩白頭佬，女皇的密令呀dllm"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-05T03:42:47.000Z","msg":"係皇帝嘅聖旨，妹仔只係執行旨意<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://assets.post852.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/02/15183432/image1550226703310.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fassets.post852.com%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2019%2F02%2F15183432%2Fimage1550226703310.png&h=86b99d50&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://s.rfi.fr/media/display/aef51608-10cd-11ea-9416-005056a99247/w:1280/p:16x9/2019-06-17t102516z_2103328285_rc138cc79310_rtrmadp_3_hongkong-extradition-lam_0.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs.rfi.fr%2Fmedia%2Fdisplay%2Faef51608-10cd-11ea-9416-005056a99247%2Fw%3A1280%2Fp%3A16x9%2F2019-06-17t102516z_2103328285_rc138cc79310_rtrmadp_3_hongkong-extradition-lam_0.jpg&h=7549e26a&s={SIZE}\" />"}]}